WEBVTT


00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:01.480
I will show you how I do my bun.

00:00:01.480 --> 00:00:02.920
I use a satin scrunchie,

00:00:02.920 --> 00:00:05.320
cause it's less likely to get knotted up in my hair.

00:00:05.320 --> 00:00:05.800
And you're right,

00:00:05.800 --> 00:00:06.980
I do just throw it up,

00:00:07.240 --> 00:00:10.140
all my hair up messy,

00:00:10.760 --> 00:00:12.100
like in a ponytail.

00:00:12.320 --> 00:00:13.720
And then I pull it through,

00:00:13.720 --> 00:00:15.000
but not all the way through.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:17.860
And then pull it through again,

00:00:18.640 --> 00:00:20.260
but not all the way through again.

00:00:21.640 --> 00:00:22.200
And that's it.

00:00:22.200 --> 00:00:24.960
And then as I talk, it bops and falls down my head.

00:00:24.960 --> 00:00:27.340
And that's it.
